name: Casio Men's DW6900CC-6 G-Shock Metallic Purple Digital Sport WatchDW6900CC-6
description:
Features

    *
      Shock Resistant, 200 Meter Water Resistant, EL Backlight with Afterglow
    *
      Multi-function Alarm, 1/100 Second Stopwatch, Countdown Timer
    *
      Hourly Time Signal, Auto Calendar (pre-programmed until the year 2039), 12/24 Hour Formats
    *
      Accuracy: +/- 15 seconds per month, Battery CR2016, Approx. battery life: 2 years
    *
      Module 1289, Size of case/total weight: 53.2 x 50.0 x 16.3mm / 68g


Description
Introducing the new metallic color models from the G-Shock lineup of watches that are popular among young connoisseurs of street fashions. These new models were created by dressing up the classic styling of the DW6900 series with distinctive new colors. Each model comes with a metallic band & case and colored reverse LCD that is simple, yet striking. A glossy finish adds further impact to the coloring. Digital watch with metallic purple resin band and purple face.

name: G-Shock Men's White Resin Strap Atomic Digital Sports Watch  GW6900A-7
description:

      Receives time calibration radio signals which keep the displayed time accurate
      Auto receive function (up to 6 times per day)
      Manual receive function
      Signal:  US WWVB, UK MSF, Germany DCF77, Japan JJY40/JJY60, China BPC
      Frequency:  US 60kHz, UK 60kHz, Germany 77.5kHz, Japan 40/60kHz, China BPC 68.5kHz
    * Tough Solar Power
    * Shock Resistant
    * 200M Water Resistant
    * Full Auto EL Backlight with Afterglow
    * World Time
      31 times zones (48 cities + UTC), city code display, daylight saving on/off
    * 4 Daily alarms and 1 Snooze Alarm
      Hourly time signal
      1/100 second stopwatch
      Measuring capacity: 23:59'59.99"
      Measuring mode: Elapsed time, split time, 1st-2nd place times
      Countdown Timer
      Measuring unit: 1 second
      Input range: 1 minute to 24 hours (1-minute incremants and 1-hour increments)
    * Full auto-calendar (pre-programmed until the year 2099)
    * 12/24 hour formats
    * Button operation tone on/off
    * Accuracy: +/- 15 seconds per month
    * Storage battery: Solar rechargeable battery
    * Battery power indicator
    * Power saving function
    * Approx. battery life: 10 months on full charge (without further exposure to light)
    * Module: 3179
